title: American Beef Packers, Inc. Recalls Raw Beef Products Deemed Unfit for Human Consumption
summary: WASHINGTON, Aug. 31, 2019 American Beef Packers, Inc., a Chino, Calif. establishment, is recalling approximately 24,428 pounds of raw beef products that are deemed unfit for human consumption, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today. FSIS inspection personnel retained...
